topic.title: ARCADIA's mission statement
topic.body: ARCADIA. While it had humble origins, it has become one of the biggest online organizations ever to grace the internet. What we do is quite special. You know that. You can trust us. We will do whatever it takes to accomplish our mission. Thanks for checking us out, and remember: ARCADIA is forever.
